title: Almay Toner 2, for Dry Skin with Cucumber, 5.1-Ounce bottles
description: Step 2 of the Almay 3-step facial care system. Cleanse - tone - moisturize. Clears away impurities without drying skin. Improves skin tone; helps skin absorb moisturizer. Infused with cucumber to help hydrate and replenish skin. Hypoallergenic. Won' t clog pores. Made in USA with US and non-US components.

title: L'Oreal Paris Go 360 Clean Deep Exfoliating Scrub, 6.0 Fluid Ounce
description: Go 360 Clean offers a complete range of four expertly formulated, high-foam cleansers that are perfectly calibrated to perform with the Scrublet. The Deep Exfoliating Scrub is a gentle yet effective scrub, which exfoliates skin with natural apricot seed powder and salicylic acid to reveal perfectly clean, smoother skin. With a rich lather and fruity, apricot fragrance, this exfoliating scrub is gentle enough for daily use.

title: Coastal Scents 10 Piece Professional Blush Palette
description: This palette comes with 6 in a beautiful sheen of shimmer and 4 matte blushes.
